.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/HLDM/110%2c%e8%8a%b1%e5%8e%9f%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c244%2c20211116%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"HLDM,110,花原交簡,244,20211116,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"花原交簡","JNO":"244","JDATE":"20211116","JTITLE":"公共危險"}